nodes.title: Positive Prompt
widgets_values: A digital painting capturing a solitary, colossal Zerg-inspired bio-cruiser with a more predatory, forward-swept design. Sharp, blade-like carapace formations in dark purple and obsidian black define its aggressive silhouette. Exposed muscle fibers and glowing green nerve clusters run along its spine. Banks of organic weapon systems are clustered near the front, potentially dripping ichor or leaking bio-plasma. It hovers ominously above the rings of a gas giant. Focus on immense scale, aggressive organic design, speed (implied), and its role as a Zerg war beast.
